data.title: WENDY'S GOOD
data.text: It's always a pleasure to stop in most of these "W" eateries, in this area !!  (Not necessarily so everywhere!!). As expected, it's a "CCC" place. (CLEAN-Courteous & Competent servers/facility.) This our fav stoppin Off place traveling NATCHER Parkway, or US 68 Ky 80 west.
